## ğŸ“¦ Installation  

```bash
# Create a project
mkdir my_project && cd my_project

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv .venv

# Activate it
source .venv/bin/activate   # Mac/Linux
.venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows

# Install the SDK
pip install openai-agents

# Install dotenv for environment variables
